366
00:28:35.634 --> 00:28:38.011
Wat?
-De andere, leukere jij.


367
00:28:39.429 --> 00:28:41.306
Sparkle, ga lunchen.

368
00:28:41.473 --> 00:28:44.476
Jij komt mee.
